title: Episode #60 - Todd & Tyler & ME
description: Mike Tyler and Todd Brandt are "Todd-n-Tyler" Hosts of the Todd-N-Tyler Radio Empire, the #1 rated radio morning in Omaha, Nebraska.  We hang out and talk comedy, great road comics, their career in radio, and how much money radio show hosts make!!!
